*Pojma* nisam imao o tome šta se događa. (I had no idea what was happening.)

Nisam imao *pojma* o tome zašto su bili tu. (I had no clue why they were there.)

*Pojmu* nisam imao koliko je to koštalo. (I had no idea how much it cost.)

Tokom celog dana nisam imala *pojma* šta se događa. (I had no idea what was going on all day.)

Nisam imala *pojma* gde se nalazi taj lokal. (I had no idea where that place was.)